Third-party code and licenses
=============================

This project is MIT-licensed (see LICENSE). It contains or builds on the
following third-party work:

1. DERO AstroBWTv3 reference implementation
   - internal/astrobwt/pow.go, rc4.go and internal/refpow/ are ported from
     derohe (github.com/deroproject/derohe, astrobwt/astrobwtv3), DERO
     Foundation. See internal/astrobwt/LICENSE-DERO.txt for the DERO license
     that covers the ported hash core.

2. Go standard library (BSD-3-Clause)
   - internal/astrobwt/sais.go and sais2.go derive from Go's
     index/suffixarray SA-IS implementation.
     Copyright (c) The Go Authors. https://go.dev/LICENSE

3. v1.14 descriptor suffix array
   - internal/astrobwt/sa_v114*.go is a pure-Go port of the structure-aware
     suffix array from github.com/Dirtybird99/Dirtybird-Zig-Miner
     (vendor/v114, MIT), itself derived from the dirtybird C++ miner.

4. Go module dependencies (see go.mod; fetched at build time, not vendored)
