   - github.com/dchest/siphash (CC0/Public domain)
   - github.com/gorilla/websocket (BSD-2-Clause)
   - github.com/klauspost/cpuid/v2 (MIT)
   - github.com/minio/sha256-simd (Apache-2.0)
